snippet.title: Idle Mining Company: Idle Game - Trailer
snippet.description:
Do you like idle tycoon games?

Then the Idle Mining Company mining tycoon game is for you! This miner game is an idle simulation game where you can invest to become a rich capitalist millionaire businessman. The aim of this gold digging game is to develop your mining empire by making investments to get as much cash and idle cash as possible.

Available on Play Store:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.OnarlarGames.IdleMiningCompany

#mobilegames #idlegame
